Class VariableNode

java.lang.Object
  com.martinleopold.mode.debug.VariableNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
public class VariableNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode

Model for a variable in the variable inspector. Has a type and name and optionally a value. Can have sub-variables (as is the case for objects, and arrays).

Author:
Martin Leopold
